    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as-is. While it remains a reliable daily driver, it shows significant signs of age and use, including several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear bumper. Mechanically, the engine is functional but will likely require a tune-up soon, and the suspension has started to feel a bit loose. The interior shows visible wear on the upholstery and carpets, though it remains smoke-free. This is a solid option for someone looking for a budget-friendly vehicle who doesn't mind putting in a little work to bring it back to its best.",
