    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The exterior has some noticeable fading on the roof and hood, along with a few scuffs and door dings from regular parking lot use. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need new brakes and a tune-up in the near future. This is a solid, functional car for someone looking for transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
