    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly in showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and kept it tucked away in the garage. No scratches, no dents, and it still has that fresh new car smell! It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44500.0,
