    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 in museum condition. The S54 power plant delivers linear throttle response through its six individual throttle bodies, having recently undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement for long-term mechanical synchrony. The chassis is impeccably preserved, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement to mitigate torsional stress. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Every bushing, damper, and seal remains in peak operating condition, maintaining the factory-spec suspension geometry. This is a turnkey example for the discerning purist seeking a mechanically flawless icon.",
      "price": 48500.0,
