      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a factory-fresh appearance that must be seen to be believed. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero imperfections\u2014no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery still retains its original scent and firm texture, with no signs of wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule fully documented in a comprehensive service history. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the panoramic sunroof, operates exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Fitted with a fresh set of high-performance tires and boasting a spotless undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a showroom-quality example of this model.",
